snippet.title: PlayStation - Gourmet Action Game - Manpuku!! Nabe Kazoku (2002)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Gourmet Action Game: Manpuku!! Nabe Kazoku is an Action game, developed and published by Media Entertainment, which was released in Japan in 2002.
